asset_id.descr: Asset ID of the tokenized asset

asset_registry_id.descr: App ID of the Asset Registry managing this asset

boli_allocation.descr: Amount of BOLI tokens allocated to this asset

community_identifier.descr: Address of community/indigenous group with stewardship

community_share.descr: Percentage for community in basis points (100 = 1%)

conservation_share.descr: Percentage for ongoing conservation in basis points (100 = 1%)

current_funding.descr: Current amount of BOLI tokens funded

has_ownership_tokens.descr: Whether the asset has ownership tokens

heritage_type.descr: Type of heritage (archaeological, architectural, cultural, indigenous)

investment_status.descr: Investment status (registered, funding, funded, active, completed)

investor_share.descr: Percentage for investors in basis points (100 = 1%)

jurisdiction_code.descr: Jurisdiction code where the asset is located/regulated

last_updated.descr: Timestamp of the last update to the asset

metadata.descr: IPFS hash or other metadata reference

ownership_token_id.descr: ID of token representing fractional ownership

project_verifier.descr: Address of expert who verifies completion

treasury_app_id.descr: App ID of the Treasury managing the backing

contract.name: HeritageAssetContract

methods.name: create
methods.desc: Initialize the app - basic setup only

methods.name: configure_boli_integration
methods.desc: Configure the contract with BOLI integration

methods.name: create_heritage_asset
methods.desc: Creates a new heritage asset with BOLI allocation

methods.name: update_funding_status
methods.desc: Updates the heritage asset funding status

methods.name: register_asset_revenue
methods.desc: Register revenue generated by the heritage asset and distribute to token holders

methods.name: update_heritage_documentation
methods.desc: Update heritage asset documentation and status

methods.name: create_restoration_project
methods.desc: Create a restoration/conservation project for the heritage asset

methods.name: contribute_to_project
methods.desc: Contribute funds to a heritage restoration project

methods.name: issue_ownership_tokens
methods.desc: Issue ownership tokens for contributors based on their contribution

methods.name: distribute_community_tokens
methods.desc: Distribute ownership tokens to the community steward

methods.name: verify_phase_completion
methods.desc: Verify completion of a project phase

contract.desc: Manages tokenization, restoration funding, and cultural stewardship of heritage sites and artifacts
